Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.51,0:24:33.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.19,0:24:34.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Salt!
