Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:40.08,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:38.24,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm doing somer-salts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.75,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Talk about being salty.
